title: Improve type errors in torch.jit.trace
body_html:

    1. torch._C.GraphExecutor(func: function, inputs: List[torch::autograd::Variable], optimize: bool = True)
    2. torch._C.GraphExecutor(graph: torch::jit::Graph, optimize: bool = True)
